# TravelPlan: Vegan Eco Amsterdam Trip for Two — Cologne to Amsterdam, Oct 3–6 2026

| Day 1 — 2026-10-03 — Arrival, Vegfest, vegan dinner | Day 2 — 2026-10-04 — Canal clean-up, plant-based dining, cycling | Day 3 — 2026-10-05 — Markets, parks, vegan food tour | Day 4 — 2026-10-06 — Vegan brunch and return to Cologne |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1. ICE International: Cologne to Amsterdam** [transport] 09:40–12:20 @ Köln Hbf → Amsterdam Centraal (€60.00) — Rail-first arrival from Köln Hauptbahnhof to Amsterdam Centraal. Exact 2026 timetable not yet released; direct ICE International usually takes about 2h40 and runs frequently. Book via DB/NS International once tickets open; seat reservations recommended. — Links: [link 1](https://int.bahn.de/en/offers/saver-fare-flexible-fare/super-saver-fare-europe-netherlands), [link 2](https://www.nsinternational.com/en/train/cologne-amsterdam) | **1. Organic breakfast at hotel / Westerpark** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Conscious Hotel Westerpark, Haarlemmerweg 10, 1014 BE Amsterdam (€40.00) — Start with the hotel’s organic breakfast or a simple vegan breakfast in Westerpark before the canal clean-up. — Links: [link 1](https://conscioushotels.com/stay/westerpark) | **1. Bike ride to Albert Cuyp Market / De Pijp** [transport] 10:00–10:45 @ Conscious Hotel Westerpark → Albert Cuypstraat (€0.00) — Use the 24-hour bike rental to ride from Westerpark toward De Pijp and Albert Cuyp Market, taking a conservative pace through cycle lanes. — Links: [link 1](https://www.macbike.nl/en/), [link 2](https://amsterdam.org/en/sight/9291/albert-cuyp-market.html) | **1. Check out and store luggage at Amsterdam Centraal** [lodging] 10:30–11:30 @ Conscious Hotel Westerpark → Amsterdam Centraal luggage lockers (€12.00) — Check out by 11:00, then take bags to Amsterdam Centraal and place them in official NS luggage lockers in the East Wing or use nearby Lockerpoint if the station lockers are full. This makes the luggage plan explicit before lunch and the 15:00 train. — Links: [link 1](https://www.lockerpoint.com/lockerpoint-locations/lockerpoint-amsterdam-centraal/), [link 2](https://www.amsterdam.info/central-station/luggage-lockers/how-to-details/) |
